cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with 3D object detection and pose estimation, which are topics typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) communities. The proposed dataset and evaluation methodology also involve machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper mentions the use of geometric reasoning (cs.GR) to handle objects with symmetries.
